  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/02/pantech-vega-lte-a-gains-fingerprint-payments/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/pantech-vega-lte-a.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div>Pantech 日前在旗下 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/06/pantech-vega-lte-advanced/\">Vega LTE-A</a> 的指纹辨识技术上做了些新文章，为其加入了移动支付的功能。据悉帮助他们实现这一点的是移动支付服务供应商 Danal，他们所开发的 BarTong 应用可以让 Vega LTE-A 用户通过手机方便地消费。虽说目前该服务还只能在韩国用到，但开发者称未来在美国和中国也都有希望见到它的身影。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/02/pantech-vega-lte-a-gains-fingerprint-payments/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://thenextweb.com/asia/2013/10/02/south-korea-claims-industry-first-as-fingerprint-based-payment-lands-on-android-smartphones/\" target=\"_blank\">The Next Web</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20131001001007\" target=\"_blank\">The Korea Herald</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/02/pantech-vega-lte-a-gains-fingerprint-payments/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20736140/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/02/pantech-vega-lte-a-gains-fingerprint-payments/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
